            any website project.
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Semantic HTML structure</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
