        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Settings class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
            Technical SEO Analysis
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            Site structure, URL optimization, robots.txt, XML sitemap, canonical
